name: Dogu Inu
description: Dogu Inu is a deflationary token built on Ethereum that was created on December 10th, 2022, 3291 days after Dogecoin. It also features a Shiba Inu on it's logo, but in a form of a memeful and not that smart example. The Dogu Inu's code received 100 out of 100 points on TokenSniffer. It has an ambition to further develop into a project that's features are something more than just creative graphics and community management, but the creators haven't disclose what will it be yet.
